Welcome to GOADS, your trusted partner for premium Meta advertising assets.

This Knowledge Base is your complete resource for setting up, securing, and scaling GOADS assets, whether you are launching your first campaign or managing advertising at scale. Everything here is written to be clear and practical, so you spend less time troubleshooting and more time advertising.

We specialize in premium, hand-selected Meta assets: aged Facebook profiles, verified Business Managers, agency ad accounts, and aged Pages. Every asset is pre-verified and professionally prepared before it reaches you, delivering exceptional stability, strong ad delivery, and significantly lower disable rates from day one. Backed by reliable support and industry-leading warranties, we are built for your long-term success.

{% callout variant="tip" title="Where to begin" %}
New here? Start with the [Asset Overview](/docs/asset-overview) to choose the right asset, then follow the [Setup guide](/docs/setup-configuration/setup-asset) to get up and running safely.
{% /callout %}

### What You Will Find Here

This Knowledge Base is organized into clear categories to support you at every step:

1. **Getting Started:** What GOADS assets are, how they work, and how to get the fastest help.
2. **Asset Overview:** A breakdown of every asset type, so you can confidently choose what fits your needs.
3. **Setup Assets:** Step-by-step instructions to set up your assets, log in safely, and manage email access.
4. **Security & Solutions:** Why accounts get disabled or hacked, and the habits that keep them safe.
5. **GOADS Tools:** Custom tools and extensions that make managing assets easier and more efficient.
6. **Questions Bank:** Answers to the most common questions, grouped by topic and asset type.

Use the sidebar to browse, or the search bar on the homepage to find answers instantly.

