### GOADS Warranty Policy

We stand behind the quality of every asset we deliver with a strong, customer-friendly warranty.

1. **Facebook Profiles:** 14-day warranty with unlimited fast & free replacements if disabled under normal usage.
2. **Facebook Pages:** 14-day warranty with unlimited fast & free replacements if disabled under normal usage.
3. **Business Managers (BM):** 7-day warranty on the Business Manager itself. Native ad accounts created inside the BM are not covered.
4. **Agency Ad Accounts:** Fully covered until you successfully add a payment method and complete your first ad spend. Once spending is successful, the warranty is fulfilled.

{% callout variant="warning" title="Important Notes" %}
Warranty terms may be updated from time to time. For the most accurate, up-to-date terms, contact GOADS directly before purchasing.

To keep your warranty valid, follow our recommended setup and security guidelines. It does not cover issues caused by Meta policy violations, misuse, or improper configuration.
{% /callout %}

If anything goes wrong within the warranty period, reach out to our support team with your order details. We are committed to fast, free replacements whenever eligible.

